<subSubSection pageId="133" pageNumber="134" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="133.[151,1437,906,1652]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[269,506,1410,1437]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" pagination="7 - 79" refId="ref371337" refString="Rondani, C. (1877 b) Species italicae ordinis dipterorum (Muscaria Rndn.). Stirps XIX Sciomyzinarum revisio. Annuario della Societa dei Naturalisti di Modena, Series 2, 11 (1), 7 - 79." type="journal article" year="1877">Rondani (1877b: 65)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1877" box="[632,906,1410,1437]" class="Insecta" family="Lauxaniidae" genus="Sapromyza" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tabidiventris">
<emphasis box="[632,906,1410,1437]" italics="true" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">Sapromyza tabidiventris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
without specifying the 
<taxonomicName box="[1179,1266,1410,1436]" family="Number" pageId="133" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
, the sex or the length of the specimens, but presumably from more than 
<specimenCount box="[847,1001,1446,1473]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
because he indicated: “ 
<emphasis box="[1269,1436,1446,1472]" italics="true" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">non infrequens</emphasis>
[not rare]”. 
<bibRefCitation author="Merz, B." box="[333,532,1482,1509]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" pagination="183 - 211" refId="ref359701" refString="Merz, B. (2004) Revision of the Minettia fasciata species - group (Diptera, Lauxaniidae). Revue Suisse de Zoologie, 111 (1), 183 - 211. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 80234" type="journal article" year="2004">Merz (2004: 204)</bibRefCitation>
designated a 
<typeStatus box="[689,792,1482,1508]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">lectotype</typeStatus>
(
<specimenCount box="[808,830,1482,1508]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
) and 
<typeStatus box="[895,1057,1482,1508]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
(
<specimenCount box="[1076,1120,1482,1509]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" type="male">1 ♂</specimenCount>
, 
<specimenCount box="[1133,1197,1482,1509]" pageId="133" pageNumber="134" type="female">3 ♀♀</specimenCount>
). An additional male numbered “1553” in the MZUF (Box 29) was not included in the type series by him because “it differs in various characters from the original description”. In addition, its label is yellowish rather than the greenish color of Rondani’s original handwritten ones and is in a lower row in the Box, for which reason we treat it to be a subsequent addition.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
